{"tid":1814813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藉住今次5毛帶風向吹勇武退場，徹底放下「和」、「勇」標籤！","createTime":"2020-01-07T05:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T06:09:20.000Z","uid":4396,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82fbf706c49c509a6c439b7a6ba35fcbe0e4ee60","tid":1814813,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"你話你有家室、有負擔，所以唔敢衝，咁年輕人條命唔係命？佢地冇屋企人咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果打怪得一個人頂住所有傷害，咁就算佢再坦都好快頂唔住。但如果兩個、三個、一百個、一百萬人一起頂就可以平分傷害，減少傷亡！<br />\n<br />\n從今以後，唔好再開路俾任何人！大家一起衝、一起退！！齊上齊落呀！香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">從今以後！不提「和」、「勇」！只提「香港人」！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫我推爆佢！推上熱門同share去fb、tg、ig </span>"},{"pid":"02f819255256d46459a365fe7031d48c13417ffe","tid":1814813,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"681c52feb36355aaf5ca1e81dc163e798a4b9354","tid":1814813,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f5c1e4b790c23ab922097efcf0142b9ef43f7b6","tid":1814813,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d38e3fc77e2da2724b07ab552466918763cd4a1","tid":1814813,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8df6bb05d69ed5c1ee4e0fbd494c487240b079fe","tid":1814813,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1871e096d1a56a2047444c0f4477c570747c3b","tid":1814813,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"8c7a89a78ff21b5fead58c60016f5a60e00ae857","tid":1814813,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8